        <section id="packing">
            <h2>ESSENTIAL GEAR & PACKING</h2>
            
            <h3>Must-Have Items:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Hiking boots (broken in)</li>
                <li>Daypack (20-30L)</li>
                <li>Rain jacket (April can have showers)</li>
                <li>Sun protection (hat, sunglasses, SPF 50+)</li>
                <li>Water purification tablets</li>
                <li>First aid kit</li>
                <li>Headlamp</li>
                <li>Quick-dry clothing</li>
                <li>Warm layer (mornings are cool)</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>Available for Rent in Kathmandu:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Trekking poles: $2/day</li>
                <li>Sleeping bags: $3/day</li>
                <li>Down jackets: $5/day</li>
                <li>Complete gear shops in Thamel</li>
            </ul>
